               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I acknowledge to have pawned these<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179001130071"></xptr>articles, from motives of necessity; and when Mr. Adams had me apprehended, he wanted me to pay the money; I told him I would replace every thing; I had no intention of leaving the premises.</p>
